#, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus Base Runtime Image"
msgstr "Quarkus运行时基础镜像"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid ""
"To ease the containerization of native executables, Quarkus provides a base image providing the requirements to run these executables.\n"
"The `ubi10-quarkus-micro-image:2.0` image is:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "small (based on `ubi10-micro`)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "designed for containers"
msgstr "专为容器而设计的"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "contains the right set of dependencies (glibc, libstdc++, zlib)"
msgstr "包含正确的依赖项（glibc、libstdc++、zlib）"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "support upx-compressed executables (more details on the xref:upx.adoc[enabling compression documentation])"
msgstr "支持upx压缩的可执行文件（更多相关细节在 link:upx.html[启用压缩文档] 中）"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using the base image"
msgstr "使用此基础镜像"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "In your `Dockerfile`, just use:"
msgstr "在你的 `Dockerfile` 中，只需使用:"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Extending the image"
msgstr "扩展该镜像"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Your application may have additional requirements.\n"
"For example, if you have an application that manipulates graphics, images, or PDFs, you likely have Quarkus AWT extension included in the project and your native executable will require some additional libraries to run.\n"
"In this case, you need to use a multi-stage `dockerfile` to copy the required libraries."
msgstr "您的应用程序可能还有其他要求。例如，如果你有一个处理图形、图像或 PDF 的应用程序，你的项目中可能包含了 Quarkus AWT 扩展，而你的本地可执行文件需要一些额外的库才能运行。在这种情况下，你需要使用多级 `dockerfile` 来复制所需的库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Copying handpicked libraries makes up for a small container image, yet it is somewhat britte, differs for different base image versions, and it is a subject to change as transitive dependencies of these libraries might change."
msgstr "复制精挑细选的库可以弥补容器镜像小的不足，但这有点小题大做，不同的基础镜像版本会有不同，而且由于这些库的传递依赖关系可能会发生变化，所以复制的库也会随之变化。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Headless graphics, PDF documents, QR code images etc. manipulation is natively supported on amd64/aarch64 Linux only. Neither Windows nor MacOS are supported and require running the application in a Linux container."
msgstr "无头图形、PDF 文档、QR 码图像等操作仅在 amd64/aarch64 Linux 系统中受本机支持。不支持 Windows 或 MacOS，需要在 Linux 容器中运行应用程序。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Alternative - Using ubi-minimal"
msgstr "替代方案 - 使用 ubi-minimal"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid ""
"If the micro image does not suit your requirements, you can use https://catalog.redhat.com/en/software/containers/ubi10-minimal/66f16af45db83414cddcfc99[ubi10-minimal].\n"
"It's a bigger image, but contains more utilities and is closer to a full Linux distribution.\n"
"Typically, it contains a package manager (`microdnf`), so you can install packages more easily."
msgstr ""

