#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
msgid "To use this base image, use the following `Dockerfile`:"
msgstr "要使用该基础镜像，使用以下 `Dockerfile`:"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/quarkus-runtime-base-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To make documents processing, graphics, PDFs, etc. available for the application, you can install the required libraries using `microdnf` without manually copying anything:"
msgstr "要为应用程序提供文档处理、图形、PDF 等功能，可以使用 `microdnf` 安装所需的库，而无需手动复制任何内容："
